betterquesting:10.name:8: 检查你的资源包  ----  Checking Your Resourcepack
开始前的准备 ---- Preparation before starting
betterquesting:10.desc:8:
§c§l在游戏正式开始前，你需要做好充足的准备。现在首要的任务就是检查为本整合包准备的资源包是否成功加载。若在下一个任务中你无法看懂其文本描述，就说明你并未正确加载资源包。找到名为 §n"Isolated-Planet.zip"§r§c§l的资源包，安装完成后请点击右边的复选框，即可开启主线任务。


Before the game officially begins, you need to be well prepared. The first task now is to check if the resourcepack prepared for this integration package is successfully loaded. If you can't read the text description in the next task, it means that you didn't load the resourcepack correctly. Find the resourcepack named §n"Isolated-Planet.zip"§r§c§l. After the installation is complete, click the check box on the right to start the main line task.
